      "text": "Aid-聖-Rising HELL",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 130.29,
      "time_str": "02:10.290",
      "text": "救赎信仰后却创造了地狱",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 132.87,
      "time_str": "02:12.870",
      "text": "I'll-ness Reset-Endじゃない Burst",
      "translation": "宁愿继续战下去，直到摧毁这一切"
    },
    {
