    },
    {
      "time": 142.43,
      "time_str": "02:22.430",
      "text": "A-Z 想像High-de-Siehst YOU das?",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 142.43,
      "time_str": "02:22.430",
      "text": "从出生到流转，我是否可以揣测到你那更崇高的理想？",
